body:

Us: um, that’s nice and all but is Peter ever going to have to answer for throwing his wife and unborn child under the bus in this story? Will he ever find out what he did and actually have to deal with it?

summary: So why is this just clicking to me now while I was sleeping? Peter was 17 years old when infinity war started. Peter was 17...
body: So why is this just clicking to me now while I was sleeping? Peter was 17 years old when infinity war started. Peter was 17 years old and about to start his senior year and graduate. We missed Peter from 15-17 and missed Tony guiding him as he grew up. We missed many storylines and many possible relationship milestones between him and MJ. So for everyone saying there isn’t enough development between MJ and Peter for them to be in a relationship, that’s false. We don’t know. We don’t know what developments we may or may not have missed. We don’t know anything because we missed 2 years of Peters life before Infinity War and then Peter missed another 5 years since. I’m just-

title: Rumor: Sony Wants Tom Hardy’s Venom in Spider-Man 3, Not Deadpool
body:
Rumor: Sony Wants Tom Hardy’s Venom in Spider-Man 3, Not Deadpool

A Marvel insider claims Sony Pictures is attempting to incorporate Tom Hardy’s Venom in the third Marvel Studios-delivered Spider-Man film, contesting a report from days prior that guaranteed Disney-possessed Marvel was thinking about presenting Ryan Reynolds’ Deadpool in Spider-Man 3.

Twitter account @RogerWardell, who in December released real Avengers: Endgame spoilers that were eventually…
